
---

## 🛡️ .gitignore (suggested draft)

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.log

# Virtual environments
venv/
.env/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE configs
.vscode/
.idea/

# Debug outputs
debug_frame.png
debug_mask.png

# Assets (optional: keep only source textures)
assets/*.tmp
assets/*.bak

# Requirements lock (if generated)
requirements.lock
